CSS: Cascading Style Sheets
.HTML creates structure of our webpage
.CSS turns our boring looking HTML webpages to good looking websites.
.It is impossible to create websites without using HTML
.Version History of CSS: 1996:CSS1, 1998:CSS2, 1998:Started working on CSS3(current version), we will never get CSS4
Hakon Wium Lie, proposed the concept of CSS while working with Time Berners-Lee and Robert Cailliau at CERN in 1994